      "span_text": "This suggested that the efficiency of CCR5 usage remained unchanged regardless of the viral phenotype or disease stages. This was in agreement of earlier data showing that most primary SI viruses are dual tropic in chemokine receptor usage and can still use CCR5 efficiently [CITATION_1] ."
